Package de.chojo.universalis.worlds

package de.chojo.universalis.worlds
Basic implementation for valid FFXIV world, datacenters and regions.
  • Interface Summary
    Interface
    Description
    DataCenter
    Represetns a data center container multiple worlds
    Region
    Represents a region containing multiple datacenters
    World
    Represents a world.
    WorldProvider
    An interface which is used for entities that can provide one or more worlds.
